{"tid":1633524,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非升級：流動連儂站！！！","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T16:12:15.000Z","uid":305577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"95759bef3af6ab7e2567e357046113c8b17ea989","tid":1633524,"uid":305577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">主動出擊！！！<br />\n全民助選團上身！！！<br />\n唔再被動等街坊自己睇文宣，直接同街坊面對面溝通、將文宣重點解釋清楚！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n天琦講過：「在我從政時，我常提醒自己：政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">如何操作？<br />\n<br />\n時：人流多時段（返工/放工，朝早買餸時間，lunch time，接放學時間）<br />\n<br />\n地：各區連儂牆附近、人流多地點<br />\n<br />\n物資：連儂牆物資leaflet版、電視/laptop/iPad、speaker ... 任何幫到大家同街坊溝通嘅材料<br />\n<br />\n人：人係重點！！！最適合有耐性、鍾意同人傾計嘅和理非 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 預左要同意見不合嘅街坊熱烈討論<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n（唔係叫你撐區選參選人，當然之後臨近區選都要變陣啦）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n香港人，反抗！</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"d136ae489bd7321fe285e1cf00e94eb25166b245","tid":1633524,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:21:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">又話杯葛？<br />\n又話抗爭？<br />\n繼續俾錢佢賺去出賣港人？<br />\n和理非平時返工唔好再俾正價搭黨鐵！<br />\n無得揀嘅情況例外</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/237n0J0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F237n0J0.jpg&h=61248f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o0TeRHg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo0TeRHg.jpg&h=94f567e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RFtRTVB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRFtRTVB.jpg&h=5322f0ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dO7Z2OW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdO7Z2OW.jpg&h=925cce53&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxJ20AB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxJ20AB.jpg&h=c7141e62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFpQ9Cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJFpQ9Cb.jpg&h=a7156522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果和理非連咁小野都做唔到<br />\n就唔好學人話抗爭</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHxjrJf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHxjrJf.jpg&h=8688cd40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日<span style=\"color: red;\">全民三罷</span>！！！<br />\n當十幾歲嘅學生中槍，<br />\n咁多個人冇咗隻眼，<br />\n咁多個義士死諫，<br />\n仲可以正常返工返學？</span>"},{"pid":"e58268d607006878b2938e86d4db6b95a48e16ef","tid":1633524,"uid":305577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:21:11.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"d4273042abefa8a09115cd3e0450bea86af2e6b5","tid":1633524,"uid":305577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:21:50.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"dd676451d5f7094d3eeccc4168c4dede171a5b82","tid":1633524,"uid":305577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:22:43.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"4f